{"data":{"allBoardYaml":{"edges":[{"node":{"title":{"fi":"Puheenjohtaja","en":"Chairperson"},"name":"Santeri Hildén","email":"puheenjohtaja@as.fi","phone":"+358 504315265","telegram":"SHilderi","picture":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/jpeg;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/da19eefba1c7bd601577320febdd07cb/5a7c3/Santeri_Hilden.jpg","srcSet":"/static/da19eefba1c7bd601577320febdd07cb/f505e/Santeri_Hilden.jpg 250w,\n/static/da19eefba1c7bd601577320febdd07cb/be5ed/Santeri_Hilden.jpg 500w,\n/static/da19eefba1c7bd601577320febdd07cb/5a7c3/Santeri_Hilden.jpg 1000w,\n/static/da19eefba1c7bd601577320febdd07cb/5c8f1/Santeri_Hilden.jpg 2000w","sizes":"(min-width: 1000px) 1000px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/da19eefba1c7bd601577320febdd07cb/e7160/Santeri_Hilden.webp 250w,\n/static/da19eefba1c7bd601577320febdd07cb/5f169/Santeri_Hilden.webp 500w,\n/static/da19eefba1c7bd601577320febdd07cb/3cd29/Santeri_Hilden.webp 1000w,\n/static/da19eefba1c7bd601577320febdd07cb/62c39/Santeri_Hilden.webp 2000w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 1000px) 1000px, 100vw"}]},"width":1000,"height":1000}}},"description":{"fi":"Johtaa hallitusta ja sitä kautta koko killan toimintaa.\nOta yhteyttä puheenjohtajaan, jos asiasi koskee kiltaa tai et tiedä keneen ottaa yhteyttä.","en":"The chairperson leads the guild's board and represents the guild; they are ultimately responsible for keeping the guild's activities on track.  Contact the Chairman if your matter concerns the guild or if you don't know whom to contact."}}},{"node":{"title":{"fi":"Varapuheenjohtaja","en":"Vice Chairperson"},"name":"Eeva Järvenpää","email":"varapuheenjohtaja@as.fi","phone":null,"telegram":"eewuli","picture":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/jpeg;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/6abb6046140913fdf7814798e5183b3a/5a7c3/Eeva_Jarvenpaa.jpg","srcSet":"/static/6abb6046140913fdf7814798e5183b3a/f505e/Eeva_Jarvenpaa.jpg 250w,\n/static/6abb6046140913fdf7814798e5183b3a/be5ed/Eeva_Jarvenpaa.jpg 500w,\n/static/6abb6046140913fdf7814798e5183b3a/5a7c3/Eeva_Jarvenpaa.jpg 1000w,\n/static/6abb6046140913fdf7814798e5183b3a/5c8f1/Eeva_Jarvenpaa.jpg 2000w","sizes":"(min-width: 1000px) 1000px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/6abb6046140913fdf7814798e5183b3a/e7160/Eeva_Jarvenpaa.webp 250w,\n/static/6abb6046140913fdf7814798e5183b3a/5f169/Eeva_Jarvenpaa.webp 500w,\n/static/6abb6046140913fdf7814798e5183b3a/3cd29/Eeva_Jarvenpaa.webp 1000w,\n/static/6abb6046140913fdf7814798e5183b3a/62c39/Eeva_Jarvenpaa.webp 2000w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 1000px) 1000px, 100vw"}]},"width":1000,"height":1000}}},"description":{"fi":"Avustaa puheenjohtajaa ja hoitaa sihteerin tehtäviä. Vastaa pöytäkirjojen tekemisestä hallituksen ja killan kokouksista sekä kiltaa koskevan materiaalin arkistoinnista huolehtimisesta.","en":"Works with the chairperson and acts as the secretary. The vice chairperson is responsible for writing the minutes of the board and guild meetings, looking after the archive and badges of honor."}}},{"node":{"title":{"fi":"Rahastonhoitaja","en":"Treasurer"},"name":"Marie Heikkinen","email":"rahastonhoitaja@as.fi","phone":"+358 403536370","telegram":"maksuhairiot","picture":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/jpeg;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/4925b818585b557606963ab6a85e56b6/5a7c3/Marie_Heikkinen.jpg","srcSet":"/static/4925b818585b557606963ab6a85e56b6/f505e/Marie_Heikkinen.jpg 250w,\n/static/4925b818585b557606963ab6a85e56b6/be5ed/Marie_Heikkinen.jpg 500w,\n/static/4925b818585b557606963ab6a85e56b6/5a7c3/Marie_Heikkinen.jpg 1000w,\n/static/4925b818585b557606963ab6a85e56b6/5c8f1/Marie_Heikkinen.jpg 2000w","sizes":"(min-width: 1000px) 1000px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/4925b818585b557606963ab6a85e56b6/e7160/Marie_Heikkinen.webp 250w,\n/static/4925b818585b557606963ab6a85e56b6/5f169/Marie_Heikkinen.webp 500w,\n/static/4925b818585b557606963ab6a85e56b6/3cd29/Marie_Heikkinen.webp 1000w,\n/static/4925b818585b557606963ab6a85e56b6/62c39/Marie_Heikkinen.webp 2000w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 1000px) 1000px, 100vw"}]},"width":1000,"height":1000}}},"description":{"fi":"Huolehtii killan raha-asioista, kuten laskujen maksamisesta ja kirjanpidosta.\nOta yhteyttä rahastonhoitajaan raha-asioissa.","en":"The treasurer is responsible for taking care of the guild's finances, for instance, paying bills and bookkeeping. Contact the treasure in the financial matters."}}},{"node":{"title":{"fi":"Yrityssuhdevastaava","en":"Head of Corporate Relations"},"name":"Daniel Gorbatchev","email":"yrityssuhdevastaava@as.fi","phone":"+358 407770660","telegram":"danikorpo","picture":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/jpeg;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/8ee9ffaceace7dacaf1274b3aec9da40/5a7c3/Daniel_Gorbatchev.jpg","srcSet":"/static/8ee9ffaceace7dacaf1274b3aec9da40/f505e/Daniel_Gorbatchev.jpg 250w,\n/static/8ee9ffaceace7dacaf1274b3aec9da40/be5ed/Daniel_Gorbatchev.jpg 500w,\n/static/8ee9ffaceace7dacaf1274b3aec9da40/5a7c3/Daniel_Gorbatchev.jpg 1000w,\n/static/8ee9ffaceace7dacaf1274b3aec9da40/5c8f1/Daniel_Gorbatchev.jpg 2000w","sizes":"(min-width: 1000px) 1000px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/8ee9ffaceace7dacaf1274b3aec9da40/e7160/Daniel_Gorbatchev.webp 250w,\n/static/8ee9ffaceace7dacaf1274b3aec9da40/5f169/Daniel_Gorbatchev.webp 500w,\n/static/8ee9ffaceace7dacaf1274b3aec9da40/3cd29/Daniel_Gorbatchev.webp 1000w,\n/static/8ee9ffaceace7dacaf1274b3aec9da40/62c39/Daniel_Gorbatchev.webp 2000w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 1000px) 1000px, 100vw"}]},"width":1000,"height":1000}}},"description":{"fi":"Vastaa killan suhteista yrityksiin ja excursioiden järjestämisestä. Organisoi killan mainosmyyntiä sekä kehittää killan mainetta ja kunniaa yritysten silmissä. Johtaa killan yrityssuhdetoimikuntaa. \nOta yhteyttä yrityssuhdemestariin, jos asiasi liittyy yrityssuhteisiin.","en":"The Head of Corporate Relations leads the corporate relations committee. They advance the reputation and credit of the guild among the corporations by collaborating with them. They also organize excursions, events and sponsorships. Contact the Head of Corporate Relations if your matter concerns corporate relations."}}},{"node":{"title":{"fi":"Viestintämestari","en":"Master of Communications"},"name":"Joel Forsström","email":"viestintamestari@as.fi","phone":null,"telegram":"joel_forsstrom","picture":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/jpeg;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/252dc2179d49505e00d65b02d47927cb/5a7c3/Joel_Forsstrom.jpg","srcSet":"/static/252dc2179d49505e00d65b02d47927cb/f505e/Joel_Forsstrom.jpg 250w,\n/static/252dc2179d49505e00d65b02d47927cb/be5ed/Joel_Forsstrom.jpg 500w,\n/static/252dc2179d49505e00d65b02d47927cb/5a7c3/Joel_Forsstrom.jpg 1000w,\n/static/252dc2179d49505e00d65b02d47927cb/5c8f1/Joel_Forsstrom.jpg 2000w","sizes":"(min-width: 1000px) 1000px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/252dc2179d49505e00d65b02d47927cb/e7160/Joel_Forsstrom.webp 250w,\n/static/252dc2179d49505e00d65b02d47927cb/5f169/Joel_Forsstrom.webp 500w,\n/static/252dc2179d49505e00d65b02d47927cb/3cd29/Joel_Forsstrom.webp 1000w,\n/static/252dc2179d49505e00d65b02d47927cb/62c39/Joel_Forsstrom.webp 2000w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 1000px) 1000px, 100vw"}]},"width":1000,"height":1000}}},"description":{"fi":"Vastaa jäsenistön tiedottamisesta lähettämällä tiedotteita ja ylläpitämällä kalenteria. Viestintämestari pitää ajan tasalla myös killan sähköpostilistoja ja nettisivujen sisältöä.\nOta yhteyttä viestintämestariin halutessasi tiedottaa killisteille jotakin.","en":"The Master of Communications keeps guild members informed about various events and other interesting and important matters. They take care of the guild's channels of communication, email lists, calendar and website, in addition to which they also send a weekly bulletin that explain what is happening and where. Contact the Master of Communication when you want to share information to the guild members."}}},{"node":{"title":{"fi":"Fuksikapteeni","en":"Fuksi Captain"},"name":"Milja Jänis","email":"fuksikapteeni@as.fi","phone":null,"telegram":"kalavelho","picture":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/jpeg;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/76f7236c97bea784248b8e97cfb58cf3/5a7c3/Milja_Janis.jpg","srcSet":"/static/76f7236c97bea784248b8e97cfb58cf3/f505e/Milja_Janis.jpg 250w,\n/static/76f7236c97bea784248b8e97cfb58cf3/be5ed/Milja_Janis.jpg 500w,\n/static/76f7236c97bea784248b8e97cfb58cf3/5a7c3/Milja_Janis.jpg 1000w,\n/static/76f7236c97bea784248b8e97cfb58cf3/5c8f1/Milja_Janis.jpg 2000w","sizes":"(min-width: 1000px) 1000px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/76f7236c97bea784248b8e97cfb58cf3/e7160/Milja_Janis.webp 250w,\n/static/76f7236c97bea784248b8e97cfb58cf3/5f169/Milja_Janis.webp 500w,\n/static/76f7236c97bea784248b8e97cfb58cf3/3cd29/Milja_Janis.webp 1000w,\n/static/76f7236c97bea784248b8e97cfb58cf3/62c39/Milja_Janis.webp 2000w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 1000px) 1000px, 100vw"}]},"width":1000,"height":1000}}},"description":{"fi":"Vastaa killan fuksikasvatuksesta ja -toiminnasta. Järjestää fuksitapahtumia killan, korkeakoulun sekä yliopiston muiden fuksikapteenien kanssa. Toimii esimerkkinä ja tukena fukseille. Työskentelee yhteistyössä ISOpomon kanssa.","en":"The Fuksi Captain is responsible for all fuksi wellbeing and fuksi events. They organize events for fuksis with other guild members, the University and other Fuksi Captains. Collaborates closely with the Tutor Coordinator."}}},{"node":{"title":{"fi":"Fuksikapteeni","en":"Fuksi Captain"},"name":"Elsa Kuntsi","email":"fuksikapteeni@as.fi","phone":null,"telegram":"saippuamarja","picture":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/jpeg;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/9370942584b2d4a35f4d31887df3b22d/5a7c3/Elsa_Kuntsi.jpg","srcSet":"/static/9370942584b2d4a35f4d31887df3b22d/f505e/Elsa_Kuntsi.jpg 250w,\n/static/9370942584b2d4a35f4d31887df3b22d/be5ed/Elsa_Kuntsi.jpg 500w,\n/static/9370942584b2d4a35f4d31887df3b22d/5a7c3/Elsa_Kuntsi.jpg 1000w,\n/static/9370942584b2d4a35f4d31887df3b22d/5c8f1/Elsa_Kuntsi.jpg 2000w","sizes":"(min-width: 1000px) 1000px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/9370942584b2d4a35f4d31887df3b22d/e7160/Elsa_Kuntsi.webp 250w,\n/static/9370942584b2d4a35f4d31887df3b22d/5f169/Elsa_Kuntsi.webp 500w,\n/static/9370942584b2d4a35f4d31887df3b22d/3cd29/Elsa_Kuntsi.webp 1000w,\n/static/9370942584b2d4a35f4d31887df3b22d/62c39/Elsa_Kuntsi.webp 2000w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 1000px) 1000px, 100vw"}]},"width":1000,"height":1000}}},"description":{"fi":"Vastaa killan fuksikasvatuksesta ja -toiminnasta. Järjestää fuksitapahtumia killan, korkeakoulun sekä yliopiston muiden fuksikapteenien kanssa. Toimii esimerkkinä ja tukena fukseille. Työskentelee yhteistyössä ISOpomon kanssa.","en":"The Fuksi Captain is responsible for all fuksi wellbeing and fuksi events. They organize events for fuksis with other guild members, the University and other Fuksi Captains. Collaborates closely with the Tutor Coordinator."}}},{"node":{"title":{"fi":"Master's and International Student Captain","en":"Master's and International Student Captain"},"name":"Jere Hasu","email":"misc@as.fi","phone":null,"telegram":"JereHa","picture":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/jpeg;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/42e7a5eb0f1bb41c0edd8582da93acd0/5a7c3/Jere_Hasu.jpg","srcSet":"/static/42e7a5eb0f1bb41c0edd8582da93acd0/f505e/Jere_Hasu.jpg 250w,\n/static/42e7a5eb0f1bb41c0edd